  "description": "A retro arcade high-score screen turned business dashboard: deep CRT black-blue, insert-coin red, pixel-yellow score highlights and 1-up green, Press Start 2P headings with VT323 score readouts over a clean Jost body. Flashy in the chrome, dead-serious in the data.",
